The output MUST be a JSON object with a single key 'data', which is a list of dictionaries.
Each dictionary should represent a record, with the keys in each dictionary corresponding to the keys mentioned above.

Example format:
{
    "data": [
        { "name": "B.Tech CS", "description": "...", "duration": "4 Years", "rigour": "...", "tuition": "...", "career": "...", "course group": "...", "course domain": "..." }
    ]
}
RETURN ONLY JSON. NO MARKDOWN.
